FT  26 AUG 92 / UK Company News: River &amp; Mercantile Smaller value down
River &amp; Mercantile Smaller Companies Trust had a net asset value of 99.27p
per share at July 31 against 105.53p a year earlier.
Net revenue for the year fell from Pounds 1.23m to Pounds 924,000 for
earnings per share of 3.69p (4.93p). A final dividend of 2.65p is
recommended for a total of 3.9p (4.12p including special of 0.37p).
